text: is a Japanese football player. She played for the Japan national team. ==Biography== Kuno was born in Fujisawa on December 27, 1989. After graduating from Musashigaoka College, she joined INAC Kobe Leonessa in 2010. She moved to Iga FC Kunoichi in 2012.Iga FC Kunoichi She plays 70 matches in Nadeshiko League. In 2018, she moved to Nojima Stella Kanagawa Sagamihara. In March 2013, Kuno was selected the Japan national team for 2013 Algarve Cup.
